= Steam Condenser

The Steam Condenser is a multi-language library for querying Source and GoldSrc
game servers as well as the Steam master servers. Currently it is implemented in
Java, PHP and Ruby.

== Requirements

* Linux, MacOS X or Windows
* Java 1.4 or newer

